      "seed": 769855708,
      "version": 2797,
      "versionNonce": 2135300452,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771947965644,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "9 - They req the LLM to provide the response.",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "9 - They req the LLM to provide the response.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "8M4MU2EVOM6nsuXL3AK_r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6462.239408772571,
      "y": 1737.6665901203498,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 219.00000000000023,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1821511780,
      "version": 2936,
      "versionNonce": 1735745787,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011757189,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "10 - When the LLMs plan, there are series of\nsmaller prompts automatically created in the\ncontext.",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "10 - When the LLMs plan, there are series of smaller prompts automatically created in the context.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "ujImzILEn1kkyWAH7vr7I",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6462.239408772571,
      "y": 2034.6665901203503,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 146.00000000000014,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1r",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1348562396,
      "version": 3096,
      "versionNonce": 1035307419,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011757189,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "11 - When the smaller prompt req is sent to\nLLMs, the tool calls come out in the response.",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "11 - When the smaller prompt req is sent to LLMs, the tool calls come out in the response.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "ixPV26nIFEB0CG9ghMGEE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6462.239408772571,
      "y": 2271.1665901203496,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 219.00000000000023,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1s",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 403641436,
      "version": 3254,
      "versionNonce": 1999085115,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011757189,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "12 - Tool or function is executed, and\nresponse is sent to LLM with the output.\nWhich the LLM can take as context",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "12 - Tool or function is executed, and response is sent to LLM with the output. Which the LLM can take as context",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "Wpa1Yvos4yiizYjjqq3Fl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6462.239408772571,
      "y": 2569.666437532459,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 219.00000000000023,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1t",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1422597988,
      "version": 3448,
      "versionNonce": 783163099,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011757189,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "13 - If the current smaller prompt finishes\nalso, there is a logic to continue to the next\ntask.",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "13 - If the current smaller prompt finishes also, there is a logic to continue to the next task.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "irElZ8HlN_6DwbJpmJDww",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7788.905617675568,
      "y": 1339.6665901203496,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 292.0000000000003,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1u",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 777108700,
      "version": 3728,
      "versionNonce": 675314101,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011748109,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "13 - When the skill is sent in as the context, it\ncontains the steps that needs to be executed,\nand each of these steps can contain tools or\ncommands",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "13 - When the skill is sent in as the context, it contains the steps that needs to be executed, and each of these steps can contain tools or commands",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "xv8s3HCOOuq0gpFTtTJaZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7788.905617675568,
      "y": 1676.333307649647,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 219.00000000000023,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1v",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1215841892,
      "version": 3839,
      "versionNonce": 1305574165,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011748109,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "14 - Skill also contains the instructions that\nLLM has to follow in order to reach the finish\ntoken",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "14 - Skill also contains the instructions that LLM has to follow in order to reach the finish token",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "DSZzWO75w3oaEMJsSYa4i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7788.905617675568,
      "y": 1977.9998725910532,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 146.00000000000014,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1404054884,
      "version": 3994,
      "versionNonce": 902322395,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772000151439,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "15 - This means we can get any sequential\nwork done, and any script can be called.",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "15 - This means we can get any sequential work done, and any script can be called.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "_HpFco8BfzfHEX-jODzsD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7788.905617675568,
      "y": 2180.6108751952197,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 146.00000000000014,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
