      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011748109,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "16 - These scripts we are calling can have \ndeterministic output",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "16 - These scripts we are calling can have \ndeterministic output",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "pg41g7IiA7JylH_pdJJnY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7788.905617675568,
      "y": 2388.944157665923,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 438.00000000000045,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1553509424,
      "version": 4498,
      "versionNonce": 2114157013,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772011748109,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "17 - The Thought, action, Observation loop\ncan be executed using the agent. It starts by\nLLM thinking, and giving the tool to call.\nThen tool is executed where the action occurs.\nFollowing that context is sent back, for LLM\nobservation.",
      "fontSize": 54.07407407407412,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "17 - The Thought, action, Observation loop can be executed using the agent. It starts by LLM thinking, and giving the tool to call.\nThen tool is executed where the action occurs.\nFollowing that context is sent back, for LLM observation.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "4ixlbAaRcACHM1eLwIM_T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7788.905617675568,
      "y": 2858.944157665923,
      "width": 1140.7863866412472,
      "height": 219.00000000000023,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
